    <title>Markdown 语法</title>
    <url>/2023/08/25/Markdown-%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>初学markdown语法</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<p>####标题</p>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="line">依次类推</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####文本格式</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体文本*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗文本**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*加粗并斜体文本*</span>**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`高亮`</span>文本</span><br><span class="line">~~删除文本~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####引用</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; <span class="strong">**开始引用**</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; <span class="emphasis">*换行一次*</span> <span class="strong">**仍在引用**</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; <span class="emphasis">*换行两次*</span> <span class="strong">**引用结束**</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>######示例</p>
<figure class="highlight node-repl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">微型计算机系统</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; 硬件系统</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 中央处理器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 存储器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 内存</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 外存</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 输入设备</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 键盘</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 鼠标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 输出设备</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 显示器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; &gt; 打印机</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; 软件系统</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 系统软件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span> <span class="language-javascript">&gt; &gt; 应用软件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>######效果</p>
<blockquote>
<p>微型计算机系统</p>
<blockquote>
<p>硬件系统</p>
<blockquote>
<p>中央处理器</p>
<p>存储器</p>
<blockquote>
<p>内存</p>
<p>外存</p>
</blockquote>
<p>输入设备</p>
<blockquote>
<p>键盘</p>
<p>鼠标</p>
</blockquote>
<p>输出设备</p>
<blockquote>
<p>显示器</p>
<p>打印机</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<p>软件系统</p>
<blockquote>
<p>系统软件</p>
<p>应用软件</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<p>####列表</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">使用1.作为开始，会自动设置序号。子列表前添加四个空格即可。</span><br><span class="line">可以使用* / + / - 作为开始。</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 一级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   1.</span> 二级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   2.</span> 二级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      3.</span> 三级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      4.</span> 三级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 一级列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 一级列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####表格</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">左对齐</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">:----------</span></span><br><span class="line">右对齐</span><br><span class="line">----------:</span><br><span class="line">居中对齐</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">:----------</span><span class="symbol">:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>######示例</p>
<figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 课程表 </span>|<span class="string"> 星期一  </span>|<span class="string">  星期二  </span>|<span class="string">  星期三  </span>|<span class="string"> 星期四  </span>|<span class="string">  星期五  </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> :----: </span>|<span class="string"> :-----: </span>|<span class="string"> :------: </span>|<span class="string"> :------: </span>|<span class="string"> :-----: </span>|<span class="string"> :------: </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">  上午  </span>|<span class="string">  Math   </span>|<span class="string"> Chinese  </span>|<span class="string">  Music   </span>|<span class="string">  Math   </span>|<span class="string"> Chinese  </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">  下午  </span>|<span class="string"> Chinese </span>|<span class="string">    PE    </span>|<span class="string">   Math   </span>|<span class="string"> English </span>|<span class="string"> Computer </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 晚自习 </span>|<span class="string"> English </span>|<span class="string"> Computer </span>|<span class="string"> Computer </span>|<span class="string">  Math   </span>|<span class="string"> Chinese  </span>|</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>######效果</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">课程表</th>
<th align="center">星期一</th>
<th align="center">星期二</th>
<th align="center">星期三</th>
<th align="center">星期四</th>
<th align="center">星期五</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">上午</td>
<td align="center">Math</td>
<td align="center">Chinese</td>
<td align="center">Music</td>
<td align="center">Math</td>
<td align="center">Chinese</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">下午</td>
<td align="center">Chinese</td>
<td align="center">PE</td>
<td align="center">Math</td>
<td align="center">English</td>
<td align="center">Computer</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">晚自习</td>
<td align="center">English</td>
<td align="center">Computer</td>
<td align="center">Computer</td>
<td align="center">Math</td>
<td align="center">Chinese</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>####代码块</p>
<figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">以```开始和结束</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####链接</p>
<figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[博客主页]</span>(<span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//yesright.cn)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[follow me](<span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//github.com/study-harder)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####图片</p>
<figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![头像](https:<span class="regexp">//gi</span>tee.com<span class="regexp">/yesright/</span>blogimage<span class="regexp">/raw/m</span>aster<span class="regexp">/img/</span>avatar.png)</span><br><span class="line">![头像](<span class="regexp">/img/</span>avatar.png)  <span class="regexp">//</span>可以用相对地址，此处没有对应图片所以无法显示</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####分割线</p>
<figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">使用三个或三个以上的* <span class="regexp">/ + /</span> - / _来建立分割线</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">++++</span><br><span class="line">-----</span><br><span class="line">______</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>####转义符</p>
<figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在markdown的语法里面，使用了一些特定的符号作为语法:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\</span> `  * _ &#123;&#125; [] () <span class="comment"># + - . !</span></span><br><span class="line">如果我们想输出符号，而不是被识别成语法，就需要使用转义字符 <span class="string">\</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/.io//1.png" alt="示例"></p>
]]></content>
